      "id": "an_8bb2f90f",
      "reference_id": "32b4315e-6da0-4106-b475-092b9a15779d",
      "text": "Authors make a comparison between expert-derived features versus automatically engineered features (AutoML) to predict group interactions from classroom videos. ",
      "provenance": {
        "page_id": "32b4315e-6da0-4106-b475-092b9a15779d"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "an_baa994c8",
      "reference_id": "32b4315e-6da0-4106-b475-092b9a15779d",
      "text": "The results show that combining both feature extraction methods outperforms the use of exclusive manual expert feature engineering. Authors follow-up with an analysis of feature importance even though, at this stage, they make no explicit mention on what were the moist important features. ",
      "provenance": {
        "page_id": "32b4315e-6da0-4106-b475-092b9a15779d"
      }
    }
